c.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608710/extras/25aee85ac67834881fdc94a87f88f51b.poster.avif?t=1659108390\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608710/extras/25aee85ac67834881fdc94a87f88f51b.webm?t=1659108390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608710/extras/25aee85ac67834881fdc94a87f88f51b.mp4?t=1659108390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
